data.description: Welcome to this ideal Ranch located in Concord, with a walkout basement, extra full kitchen in the lower area and with a separate entrance that can be used as a separate living suite, additional 4th bedroom on the lower level, 3 full and 1 half baths, 2 fireplaces, and main living laundry room. This home sits on over .51 acres and has tons of space in the backyard. The kitchen has been recently updated and has plenty of counter space, stainless steel appliances, white subway tile backsplash, lots of cabinet storage, and a coffee bar area that can also be used as an additional desk area. The owners' suite has a large walk-in closet, sliding door which has access to the deck and an en-suite bath with a double vanity, soaking tub and shower. There is a large upper deck that is perfect for entertaining. UPDATES include: furnace and AC, replaced flooring throughout the home, and added a April Aire humidifier with UV light for air purifier. Conveniently located near I-90, Great Lakes Mall, local parks restaurants, shopping, and many other attractions. Included are ALL kitchen appliances and washer/dryer. This home is in a great location and a must see!
